928e90b0c85afb7f63586","tid":1335072,"uid":4496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:29:43.000Z","msg":"書展係重要變數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edad6bda5d614053381006d9ad39dcff4e43fd63","tid":1335072,"uid":281948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"唔需要一路守一路退，灣仔太凶險。<br />\n行完要直接走。<br />\n警方北面注重兵守實（水炮車）<br />\n東面一過界就名正言順咁捉人。<br />\n西面遊行龍尾未退未散<br />\n我地去南面就會被圍死。<br />\n警方慢慢收網就game over<br />\n留守的人都會被打一身<br />\n無必要畀警方提升士氣，復仇成功"},{"pid":"44954f672f07cf0bd9cb226398143557c579e17d","tid":1335072,"uid":151578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:07:07.000Z","msg":"721見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35136ad5020c25c839707b2288169c91103bc45f","tid":1335072,"uid":281948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:08:05.000Z","msg":"[721] 唔好睇小灣仔地形<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1334006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1334006</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d6a4ee809b243e89e95377a8ac900ecad80a4107","tid":1335072,"uid":281948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:08:33.000Z","msg":"推返上熱門畀多d 留意呀"},{"pid":"11210c4f09fb70e2427677b26d55a999caa901d8","tid":1335072,"uid":281948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:09:19.000Z","msg":"好多三毛出 9 post 蓋晒有用post 呀"},{"pid":"ff78305267a5b8bd603de4c8930f58f34bf593e8","tid":1335072,"uid":213781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:10:46.000Z","msg":"721新香港"}]}